the truth is that there will be new depths (of horror) again as long as this awful and evil campaign of terrorism and revenge continues,'' king told the commons on monday. ``it has got to stop.''
there were new calls for another attempt to find agreement between the province's mainstream catholic and protestant political parties to stop guerrilla groups
