the same things that played havoc yesterday was responsible for today's games as well,'' said nauman barakat, energy futures analyst with smith barney harris upham &amp; co., new york
west texas intermediate crude oil was 40 cents lower to 11 cents higher, with april at $16.09 per 42-gallon barrel; heating oil was 30 cents to 95 cents higher, with april at 46.26 cents a gallon; and unleaded gasoline was 21 cents to 47 cents higher, with april at 46.32 cents a gallon
